Package: OpenAIR
Type: Package
Title: Integrate OpenAI's Large Language Models Into Your R Workflows
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(person("Ulrich", "Matter", email = "umatter@protonmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre")), person("Jonathan", "Chassot", email = "jonathan.chassot@unisg.ch", role = "aut"))
Maintainer: Ulrich Matter <umatter@protonmail.com>
Description: OpenAIR builds on OpenAI's API as backend and provides R wrapper functions for the ChatGPT endpoint as well as various high-level functions to integrate ChatGPT's functionality in a variety of data handling and data analytics tasks, ranging from data cleaning to the automated generation of analytics scripts.
